# 🥁 Drumpy 🎵

Keyboard drums with pygame

Keymap, sound files and volumes settings are in ```drumpy/static/keymap.yaml```

Sound samples are in ```drumpy/static/samples```

## Install
```shell script
pip install -U drumpy
```

## Run
```shell script
drumpy
```

